<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA86">
<l>peṟiṉum piṟitiyātum vēṇṭē namakkī</l>
<l>tuṟiṉu muṟātoḻiyu mēṉuñ - ciṟituṇartti</l>
<l>maṟṟorukaṇ neṟṟimēl vaittāṉṟaṉ pēyāya</l>
<l>naṟkaṇatti loṉṟāya nām</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if we obtain we shall want nothing else, whether we experience it</l>
<l>or whether this will remain unexperienced by us, having recalled a little,</l>
<l>– we who have been one in the good group that is the demonesses</l>
<l>of him who put another eye on [his] front.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
